This paper is likely to belong to the category of Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) as it discusses logical frameworks and reasoning about formal systems. It may also belong to Programming Languages (cs.PL) as it deals with higher-order abstract syntax. Software Engineering (cs.SE) is another possible category as the paper discusses the design of an open repository for evaluating and comparing different systems and libraries. Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) is also a possibility as the paper deals with reasoning about languages. Finally, Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the evaluation and comparison of different systems and libraries, which may involve the use of data structures and algorithms.
